

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>SenseBagPack</title>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Potta+One&family=Pacifico&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4, #fbc2eb, #a1c4fd, #c2e9fb);
      background-size: 500% 500%;
      animation: moverFondo 12s ease infinite;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    @keyframes moverFondo {
      0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
      50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
      100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    }

    header {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.5rem 4rem;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .logo-container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .logo-container img {
      height: 80px;
      width: auto;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .logo-container img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.08);
    }

    .logo-text {
      font-family: 'Potta One', cursive;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #b84c65;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    /* BOTÓN MENÚ */
    .menu-btn {
      font-size: 28px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .menu-btn:hover {
      color: #ff6f61;
      transform: scale(1.2);
    }

    .menu-container {
      position: relative;
    }

    /* MENÚ */
    .menu {
      display: none;
      position: absolute;
      right: 0;
      top: 50px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      width: 200px;
      box-shadow: 0px 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .menu a {
      display: block;
      padding: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .menu a:hover {
      background-color: #ff6f61;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    section {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    section:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      color: #222;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    p {
      max-width: 750px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: #444;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1.8rem;
      background-color: #ff6f61;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.9rem 1.8rem;
      border-radius: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(255, 111, 97, 0.4);
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #fff;
      color: #ff6f61;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 111, 97, 0.6);
      transform: scale(1.07);
    }

    footer {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <div class="logo-container">
    <span class="logo-text">SenseBagPack</span>
  
    <img src="/Sensebagpack/imagenes/loguito.png" alt="Logo del sistema" />
  
</div>
  <div class="menu-container">
    <div class="menu-btn" onclick="toggleMenu()">☰</div>

    <div id="menu" class="menu">
      <a href="/Sensebagpack/vistas/usuario.jsp">Acceder</a>
      <a href="/Sensebagpack/vistas/elegirnos.jsp">¿Por qué elegirnos?</a>
      <a href="/Sensebagpack/vistas/contacto.jsp">Contacto</a>
       <a href="/Sensebagpack/vistas/contacto.jsp">Objetivo</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section>
  <h2>Bienvenido a SenseBagPack</h2>
  <p>
    Un proyecto innovador que busca mejorar la movilidad y seguridad de las personas no videntes.  
    Combinamos tecnología, empatía y diseño inteligente en una mochila que detecta obstáculos y mantiene a las familias conectadas.
  </p>
  <a href="#" class="btn">Conocer más</a>
</section>




<footer>
  © 2025 SenseBagPack — Innovación con propósito.
</footer>

<script>
function toggleMenu() {
  const menu = document.getElementById("menu");
  menu.style.display = (menu.style.display === "block") ? "none" : "block";
}

window.onclick = function(event) {
  if (!event.target.matches('.menu-btn')) {
    const menu = document.getElementById("menu");
    if (menu.style.display === "block") {
      menu.style.display = "none";
    }
  }
}

</script>

</body>
</html>
